<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
  <title>Garden & Plants Blog</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.2em;
    }
    header p {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }
    main {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    section h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    section img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    section p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    /* Product Section */
    .product {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .product-item {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      flex: 1 1 calc(48% - 20px);
    }
    .product-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .product-item h4 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .product-item p {
      font-size: 1em;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    /* About Section */
    .about {
      background-color: #e9f5e9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .about h3 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
    
    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .product {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .product-item {
        flex: 1 1 100%;
      }
      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
      }
      section h2 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Garden & Plants Blog</h1>
      <p>Your source for gardening products, tips, and inspiration</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="container">
    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about">
      <h3>About Our Website</h3>
      <p>
        Welcome to Garden & Plants Blog, where our passion for gardening, sustainable living, and horticulture comes to life. Our blog is dedicated to providing you with expert tips, detailed product reviews, and inspiring ideas to create and maintain your dream garden. Whether you're just starting out or you’re an experienced gardener, we have valuable insights and quality products to help you succeed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Plants Section -->
    <section id="plants">
      <h2>Plants</h2>
      <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/1200x600/?plants" alt="Healthy Plants" />
      <p>
        Explore the best plants for your garden and learn how to care for them. From indoor greens to outdoor blooms, discover tips on growing a variety of plants in diverse climates. Check out these featured products to create a vibrant garden.
      </p>
      <div class="product">
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?indoor,plant" alt="Indoor Plant" />
          <h4>Indoor Plant Starter Kit</h4>
          <p>
            Everything you need to kickstart your indoor garden – including pots, quality soil, and a variety of plants to get you growing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?outdoor,garden" alt="Outdoor Plant" />
          <h4>Outdoor Garden Plants</h4>
          <p>
            High-quality plants curated for your outdoor space. Choose from an array of flowers, shrubs, and trees to beautify your garden.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Seeds Section -->
    <section id="seeds">
      <h2>Seeds</h2>
      <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/1200x600/?seeds,garden" alt="Garden Seeds" />
      <p>
        Starting a garden from seeds is a rewarding experience. Learn proper planting techniques and care tips to turn seeds into healthy plants. Discover our top seed kits to get started!
      </p>
      <div class="product">
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?vegetable,seeds" alt="Vegetable Seeds" />
          <h4>Organic Vegetable Seed Kit</h4>
          <p>
            A diverse collection of vegetable seeds perfect for your home garden. Includes heirloom tomatoes, cucumbers, carrots, and more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?flower,seeds" alt="Flower Seeds" />
          <h4>Wildflower Seed Mix</h4>
          <p>
            Brighten up your garden with a mix of wildflowers. Attract pollinators like bees and butterflies while enjoying vibrant blooms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Gardens Section -->
    <section id="gardens">
      <h2>Gardens</h2>
      <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/1200x600/?garden" alt="Beautiful Garden" />
      <p>
        Design and create your dream garden with expert advice on landscaping, garden styles, and maintenance tips. Explore these essential garden products that make gardening a breeze.
      </p>
      <div class="product">
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?garden,tools" alt="Garden Tools" />
          <h4>Complete Garden Tools Set</h4>
          <p>
            All the essential tools for your garden—from pruning shears to shovels. This set is designed to make gardening easier and more enjoyable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?fertilizer,garden" alt="Garden Fertilizer" />
          <h4>Organic Garden Fertilizer</h4>
          <p>
            Boost your garden’s health with our all-natural fertilizer, perfect for flowers, vegetables, and plants.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fruits Section -->
    <section id="fruits">
      <h2>Fruits</h2>
      <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/1200x600/?fruit,trees" alt="Fruit Trees" />
      <p>
        Growing fruits at home is a fun and fulfilling hobby. Discover tips on growing fruit trees, bushes, and vines in your backyard. Check out these fantastic fruit-growing kits!
      </p>
      <div class="product">
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?fruit,tree" alt="Fruit Tree" />
          <h4>Fruit Tree Starter Kit</h4>
          <p>
            Everything you need to start growing fruit trees. Choose from apples, peaches, or pears to enjoy fresh fruit at home.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?berry,bush" alt="Berry Bush" />
          <h4>Berry Bush Kit</h4>
          <p>
            Grow your own berries with ease using this starter kit, featuring blueberry, raspberry, and strawberry bushes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Flowers Section -->
    <section id="flowers">
      <h2>Flowers</h2>
      <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/1200x600/?flowers,garden" alt="Flower Garden" />
      <p>
        Flowers add color and beauty to any garden. Learn how to grow and care for a wide range of flowers—from perennials to annuals—and keep them blooming all season long.
      </p>
      <div class="product">
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?flower,seeds" alt="Flower Seeds" />
          <h4>Flowering Plant Seeds</h4>
          <p>
            Kickstart your flower garden with a mix of annual and perennial seeds that promise a burst of color.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-item">
          <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/500x300/?flower,pots" alt="Flower Pots" />
          <h4>Decorative Flower Pots</h4>
          <p>
            Showcase your blooms in style with these beautifully designed pots—perfect for patios, windowsills, and more.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Garden & Plants Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
